    <note>Liu(2) Zong [1240] Jianzhong's [3588] and Zhengzhong's [3592]  father, Zhuo's [3585] elder brother. Xue(1) Yi's [7109] grandfather-in-law. His maternal cousin (waixiong) was Dong(1) Zunhui [7075], which must mean that he was either the son of a sister of Zunhui's mother, who was Gao(1) Xingzhou's [18343] daughter, or the son of an aunt of Zunhui. Zong had administrative talent (licai). XCB, 45.12a, 47.20b, 24a, 48.15b, 49,8a, 50.16a, 51.5a, 52.16b, 55.1b, 57.4b, 61.2b, 21a; SS, 277.17a-17b. CBD, 5, 3892.</note>
